      "content": "it feels so real too... like i can actually feel the vibration in my chest when i get close to the right tone. if the range is 20-100Hz, can you give me a more specific calculation? like if i'm looking at a standard cyclonic rotation, is there a way to calculate the specific harmonic that would disrupt the torque? i want to see if i can actually dampen the rotation using sound.",
